{"as_of_date":"2026-07-18","classification_dimensions":[{"definition":"依据外部尺寸、内部结构或表面结构处于纳米尺度进行的材料类别划分；可与具体材料交叉，但不是与碳纤维产业并列的统一产业。","dimension_id":"nano-scale","dimension_type":"scale_based_material_category","evidence_refs":["NM-STD-01","NM-STD-02"],"is_industry":false,"name_zh":"纳米尺度材料类别","role":"orthogonal_classification","values":["纳米物体","纳米结构材料","不适用或待判定"]},{"definition":"按前驱体材料路线区分PAN基、沥青基、粘胶基等。","dimension_id":"precursor-route","dimension_type":"precursor_route","evidence_refs":["CF-STD-01"],"is_industry":false,"name_zh":"前驱体路线","role":"orthogonal_classification","values":["PAN基","沥青基","粘胶基","其他或待核实"]},{"definition":"按终端使用和验证场景区分应用，不把应用分支提升为产业根。","dimension_id":"application-domain","dimension_type":"application_domain","evidence_refs":["CF-COMP-01","CF-COMP-03","CF-APP-01"],"is_industry":false,"name_zh":"应用领域","role":"orthogonal_classification","values":["航空航天","风电","高压气瓶","其他工业应用"]}],"evidence_gaps":[{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-BOUNDARY","statement":"补齐官方产业、经济活动与产品分类原件；现有CF-POL-01只支撑“高性能碳纤维及制品制造”政策子集及其与完整碳纤维产业之间的边界缺口，不能证明全产业边界。","status":"open","target_node_id":"carbon-fiber-industry"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-PRECURSOR","statement":"补齐PAN、沥青基和粘胶基等前驱体路线正式资料，不能用PAN路线代表整个产业。","status":"open","target_node_id":"precursor-stage"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-PROCESS","statement":"补齐预氧化、碳化、石墨化关键设备、参数、能耗、良率与产能原件。","status":"open","target_node_id":"oxidation-carbonization"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-PRODUCTS","statement":"补齐不同碳纤维产品形态、牌号、规格和交易边界资料。","status":"open","target_node_id":"fiber-products"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-COMPOSITES","statement":"补齐织物、预制体、预浸料、拉挤材料等中间制品结构与关系。","status":"open","target_node_id":"composite-intermediates"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-APPLICATIONS","statement":"分别补齐航空、风电、氢瓶及其他应用的客户规范、采购、验证和交易证据。","status":"open","target_node_id":"application-stage"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-TESTING","statement":"建立材料测试、供应商评价、产品认证与应用验证的分层路径。","status":"open","target_node_id":"testing-certification"},{"gap_id":"CF-GAP-EHS","statement":"补齐碳纤维制造的环境、职业健康、安全和项目环评原件。","status":"open","target_node_id":"ehs-system"},{"gap_